article.description: — Austin Phyfe had 18 points and nine rebounds as Northern Iowa topped Bradley 78-72 on Sunday.
article.headline: Phyfe scores 18 to lead N. Iowa over Bradley 78-72
article.linkText: Phyfe scores 18 to lead N. Iowa over Bradley 78-72
article.story: CEDAR FALLS, Iowa -- — Austin Phyfe had 18 points and nine rebounds as Northern Iowa topped Bradley 78-72 on Sunday. Trae Berhow had 15 points for Northern Iowa (3-7, 2/3 Missouri Valley Conference). Noah Carter added 14 points. Nate Heise had 11 points. Terry Nolan Jr. had 17 points for the Braves (6-4, 0-1). Elijah Childs added 15 points and nine rebounds. Rienk Mast had 14 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
